      <p>Softwaller builds custom textile ERP for spinning, weaving, processing and garmenting units across Tirupur, Coimbatore, Erode, Karur, Salem and beyond. Live in 12-16 weeks. Includes yarn lot tracking, GST e-invoicing, job-work in/out challan, and Tamil shop-floor UI — sized to your cluster, not a generic template.</p>
